query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 5
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('admob',
'android-custom-view',
'android-gradle',
'autohotkey',
'exception-handling',
'facebook',
'image-uploading',
'maven-2',
'nfc',
'normalization',
'plone',
'search',
'singleton',
'uinavigationcontroller',
'visual-studio-2017');
